data.description: COMING SOON!  Welcome to 409 S. Perry St., Wapakoneta, OH. This home has so much to offer and there is so much potential.  3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, living room, dining room, fenced backyard and a front and back porch.  The home is in the middle of renovations, in the kitchen and there is a second shower that is plumbed, but not finished, off of the laundry and half bath that could be finished. Call me for your showing today.  More pics to come and is available for showings starting May 5, 2024.
